    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:1.1",
          "pli": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, cetasovinibandhā. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, there are these five emotional shackles. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:1.2",
          "pli": "Katame pañca? ",
          "en": "What five? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:1.3",
          "pli": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāmesu avītarāgo hoti … pe … ",
          "en": "Firstly, a mendicant isn’t free of greed for sensual pleasures. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:1.4",
          "pli": "ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca cetasovinibandhā. ",
          "en": "These are the five emotional shackles. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.1",
          "pli": "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ cetasovinibandhānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro iddhipādā bhāvetabbā. ",
          "en": "To give up these five emotional shackles you should develop the four bases of psychic power. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.2",
          "pli": "Katame cattāro? ",
          "en": "What four? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.3",
          "pli": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, ",
          "en": "It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to enthusiasm, and active effort. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.4",
          "pli": "vīriyasamādhi … ",
          "en": "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy, and active effort. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.5",
          "pli": "cittasamādhi … ",
          "en": "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to mental development, and active effort. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.6",
          "pli": "vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. ",
          "en": "They develop the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, and active effort. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.7",
          "pli": "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ cetasovinibandhānaṃ pahānāya ime cattāro iddhipādā bhāvetabbā”ti. ",
          "en": "To give up these five emotional shackles you should develop these four bases of psychic power.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.8",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:2.9",
          "pli": "Iddhipādavaggo catuttho. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:3.1",
          "pli": "Yatheva satipaṭṭhānā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:3.2",
          "pli": "padhānā caturopi ca; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:3.3",
          "pli": "Cattāro iddhipādā ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an9.92:3.4",
          "pli": "tatheva sampayojayeti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
